title: TuneUp2009..AjC
description:
TuneUp 2009
 Got a lot of unused applications on your PC? Need to clean it up? TuneUp2009 is the solution for you. From many features, choose however you like to clean up your PC.
 
 Install as a trial, then use the CD keys after(serials)
After installing as a trial, run it, on the top right of the window should have a wheel. 
 Click register/something similar to that
 After registering, rerun, it will work!

Please Remember to SEED



Remember: AjC files have ..before AjC
                         the j is lowercase.
